===Etymology===
French [[luth]], from Old French [[leüt]], probably from Provençal [[laüt]], from Arabic {{ARchar|[[عود|العود]]}} ''al-‘ūd'' ‘wood’ (probably representing a Hispano-Arabic or North African pronunciation).

